title: 11/19/21 DPS Hour 3 Jeff Van Gundy

description:
Jeff Van Gundy tells Dan that after LeBron James has played 10 games back from injury, then we should know if the Lakers are going to be good, or great. Jeff says Russell Westbrook will probably not change at this point in his career.
